EDIT: seems like I wasn't paying any attention to the warning that KSP-AVC was throwing at me: I was still using CrossFeedEnabler......

Hello,

I'm having an issue with the radialRCStank and RCStankRadialLong parts, or rather, they're not being recognized by the game.

First of all, did Squad update or modify these parts?

Somehow, older craft saves are giving me an error that those parts are missing (even though they show up in the game files). Is this something that has happened to others as well? It's the last step to recover my old save (and by extension those older craft saves as well). What's even more interesting is that some stock craft are throwing the same error (even after a full reinstall).

If necessary I can upload one of the troubled craft saves.

Edited June 1, 2020 by simtom
